headline: Is Eaton (ETN) Quietly Redefining Its Power Infrastructure Role With Data Center And Microgrid Bets?
summary: Eaton recently announced plans to open a 350,000-square-foot manufacturing campus in Henrico County, Virginia, to produce critical power distribution equipment for the rapidly growing data center market, while also securing a contract to deliver a clean-energy microgrid for the new Manchester Public Library in Connecticut. Together, these moves highlight how Eaton is deepening its role across both high-power data center infrastructure and community-scale grid-interactive energy...
